# Data Catalog
meeting 2024.07.03

```
DATA Source
[repo ICOS]
[repo ICOS]                                                            <--> researchers (outside)
[repo KDP]   ----->  indexed and described ----> Ruisdael Data Catalog <--> PIs (writing metadata, )
[repo 4TU]                                                             <--> wiki admin 
[privte drives] 
```

* purpose data catalog: find the data

* data(sets) access: 
   * **public access** data repositories: KDP, ICOS, 4TU  -> metadata -> link to data 
   * **private access**: research drive, other, ... -> metadata -> contact PI/data-steward
* Agent: people, organizations (ROR records) - 
* Sites

* define the schema and interface for dataset
(tasks for Bert and Calorine: information on Ruisdael Organizations and People, Sites)

Ruisdael data products and responsible PIs:

* [](https://knmi.data.surfsara.nl/index.php/apps/richdocuments/documents.php/index?fileId=6785324&dir=%2FRuisdael%20Observatory%2FRuisdael%20website%20%26%20campaign%20protocol)

## the humans in the loop
* PIs/data-stewards need to act and respon to requests/question
* guidelines (documentation for PI) needed  - building the Xmas tree together


